uaraka Sports Club Ground|Nairobi]] || 4 February 2007\n|}\n{{col-break}}\n\n'''Best bowling figures in an innings in ODI'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/records/bowling/best_figures_innings.html?class=2;id=15;type=team| title=Records / Netherlands / One-Day Internationals / Best bowling figures |publisher=[[ESPNcricinfo]] |accessdate=28 May 2019}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n! Player!!Score!!Opposition!!Venue!!Date\n|-\n|[[Timm van der Gugten]] || '''5/24''' || {{cr|CAN}} || [[Maple Leaf Cricket Club|King City]] || 29 August 2013\n|-\n|[[Pieter Seelaar]] || '''4/15''' || {{cr|CAN}} || [[Maple Leaf Cricket Club|King City]] || 29 August 2013\n|-\n|[[Edgar Schiferli]] || '''4/23''' || {{cr|KEN}} || [[Senwes Park|Potchefstroom]] || 19 April 2009\n|-\n|[[Ryan ten Doeschate]] || '''4/31''' || {{cr|CAN}} || [[Ruaraka Sports Club Ground|Nairobi]] || 30 January 2007\n|-\n|[[Peter Borren]] || '''4/32''' || {{cr|AFG}}  || [[Sharjah Cricket Stadium|Sharjah]] || 29 March 2012\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n'''ODI record versus other nations'''<ref name=\"ODI\"/>\n\n''Records complete to ODI #4167. Last updated 21 June 2019.''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 600px;\"\n|-\n! Opponent !! M !! W !! L !! T !! NR !! First match !! First win\n|-\n| colspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''[[List of International Cricket Council members#Full members|ICC Full members]]'''\n|-\n|align=left| {{cr|AFG}} || 6 || 2 || 4 || 0 || 0 || 30 August 2009 || 30 August 2009\n|-\n|align=left| {{cr|AUS}} || 2 || 0 || 2 || 0 || 0 || 20 February 2003 ||\n|-\n|align=left| {{cr|BAN}} || 2 || 1 || 1 || 0 || 0 || 20 July 2010 || 20 July 2010\n|-\n|align=left| {{cr|ENG}} || 3 || 0 || 3 || 0 || 0 || 22 February 1996 ||\n|-\n|align=left| {{cr|IND}} || 2 || 0 || 2 || 0 || 0 || 12 February 2003 ||\n|-\n|align=left| {{cr|IRE}} || 10 || 1 || 7 || 1 || 1 || 8 August 2006 || 5 February 2007\n|-\n|align=left| {{cr|NZL}} |